{"about_the_game":"The Questing Demo Version released!<br><br>The Questing is a single-play action 3D RPG game set in the fantasy worldview.<br>Sweep away enemies with a variety of weapons, skills and magic based on Hack &amp; Slash and Roguelite.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019820/extras/world.gif?t=1654062389\" /><br><br>Explore a wide and beautiful map. Explore towns and cities and solve various NPC quests.<br>A good reward awaits you if you solve the quest.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019820/extras/customizing.gif?t=1654062389\" /><br><br>Customize your character as you want. Create your own character by combining hair, whiskers, eyebrows, face tattoos and colors.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019820/extras/battle1.gif?t=1654062389\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019820/extras/battle2.gif?t=1654062389\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019820/extras/battle3.gif?t=1654062389\" /><br><br>Use various weapons to hunt enemies!<br>Weapons are largely divided into close-range weapons and long-range weapons. Close weapons include one-handed weapons, two-handed weapons, double-handed weapons, and extra-large swords, while distant weapons have bows!<br>Each weapon has its own motion and special skills!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019820/extras/skill.gif?t=1654062389\" /><br><br>Use various magic and skills to wipe out enemies!<br>You can use supportive magic to buff or recover during combat, and use offensive magic to wipe out enemies!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019820/page_bg_gener